<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹无法入睡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一直在想那棵摇钱树和他即将要买的各种礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我已经迫不及待地想看到我的摇钱树了。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他不能离开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你必须等到太阳升起来以后才能去那块地。”猫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，如果在太阳升起来之前去，那棵树就会死掉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狐狸同意道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，匹诺曹等了又等。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当太阳升起的时候，匹诺曹一路跑到傻瓜福地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这就是那块儿地了。”匹诺曹说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我的摇钱树在哪里呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他找遍了整个土地，但没有找到他的摇钱树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明明就是这里啊。”他疑惑不解地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许金子们忘了要长出来！还是把它们挖出来看看吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是匹诺曹开始挖他的金子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挖呀挖呀，直到他被泥土覆盖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个洞比他开始挖的那个洞要大五倍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他还是没有找到他的金子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明明就是这里啊！我的金子呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他的头顶，有个人正在嘲笑他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抬头望去，看到了蟋蟀先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在这儿干什么？”匹诺曹叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么嘲笑我？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这个傻男孩儿，匹诺曹。”蟋蟀先生回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我曾经警告过你交朋友和做决定的时候要谨慎，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是你不听我的。那只狐狸和猫已经偷走了你的金子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们现在已经跑得远远的了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不！不！”匹诺曹喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他坐在地上哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定要告诉警察，他们会帮助我的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹跑到了附近小镇的监狱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把发生的事情告诉了警察。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他们并没有帮助他找回金子，反而把他关进了监狱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈哈。真是一个傻孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看来我们又能收到小费了，是吧？”一个人向另一个人说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，你不明白。我没有做错任何事情！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拜托了！请帮我找到我的金子。”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，你这一辈子都会呆在这里面的！”狱卒笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹并不知道，这个小镇是属于那只狐狸和猫的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们收买了狱卒，并要求他们把那些被他们抢劫的人关起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为狐狸和猫，这些警察变得很有钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹一整天都坐在监狱里面。但是他并没有哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抬头看着星星说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蟋蟀先生的话是对的。我真是一个傻孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我做了许多错误的选择。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为我，金子丢了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果有人能把我救出去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从今以后我一定会做一个很乖的孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拜托了，有人在吗？我需要帮助。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我在听着。”一个甜美的声音说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，匹诺曹看到一个很小的蓝色的光飘过他的窗户。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁在那儿？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是蓝色小仙女。我保护好孩子们不受伤害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我是来帮助你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请把我从监狱里面救出去吧。”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么会在监狱里呢？”仙女问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你做错了什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没有做错什么。”匹诺曹回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是狐狸和猫骗了我。他们偷走了我的金子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是从哪里得到那些钱的？”蓝色小仙女问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我赚来的钱。”匹诺曹说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我原来在一个节目里面表演。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹的鼻子突然开始变长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没几秒钟，他的鼻子就变成了6尺长！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹惊讶地看着他的鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你爸爸同意你在剧院里表演吗？”蓝色小仙女平静地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>340166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，蓝色小仙女。”匹诺曹说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>344957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我爸爸说我可以成为一个很好的演员！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>350152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>354182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为再次撒谎，他的鼻子变得更长了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>354183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>358760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，匹诺曹的鼻子就长到了8尺长！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>358761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>365303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的鼻子怎么了？”匹诺曹尖叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>